---
// About Bill — "Meet your mentor" section. Clean Astro, no Webflow classes.
// Styling comes from bf-design-system.css (bf-about-*, loaded globally).
---
<section class="bf-section">
  <div class="bf-container">
    <div class="bf-about-grid">
      <div class="bf-about__media">
        <img src="/assets/664a5b263659c7265be280ad/664a67e526974fa9873cf4b0_home%20images-6.webp" alt="Bill Fanter at his trading desk" />
      </div>
      <div class="bf-about__copy">
        <span class="bf-eyebrow">Meet your mentor</span>
        <h2 class="bf-h2" style="margin-top:24px">Hi, I'm Bill. I'm excited to get to know you.</h2>
        <p style="margin-top:28px">Over a 35-year career, I became one of the most sought-after executive-level bankers in the industry. I spearheaded the management of some of the largest multi-billion-dollar banks in America, and also taught at the CBA Executive Banking School.</p>
        <p>I've spent thousands of hours and thousands of dollars learning what actually works in the options market &mdash; and I've distilled it into a system that anyone serious about their financial future can follow.</p>
        <p>My goal is simple: make you successful.</p>
        <div class="bf-about__actions">
          <a class="bf-btn bf-btn--primary" href="/contact">Book a Call</a>
          <a class="bf-btn bf-btn--ghost" href="/contact">Get in Touch</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .bf-about__actions {
    margin-top: 32px;
    display: flex;
    gap: 12px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
</style>
